AUDIO: 'again. And I got the result. I am not sure about the likeness, but I guess cartoons are always different. I will do more experiments in the next tool and that should work better.'

[10:49] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'But, a tool like this can save you some time if you do the same things over and over again. You create a tool, press generate and it does all that for you. So, once you are happy with the tool, you press done and that is saved. Now,'

